---
description: All AI interaction through Gemini Live API WebSocket only
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

ALL AI interaction (equipment identification, diagnosis, conversational guidance) goes through the Gemini Live API WebSocket.

Do NOT:
- Create REST API endpoints that call Gemini
- Use the Gemini generateContent REST API
- Add `google-genai` or any Gemini SDK to the backend
- Add WebSocket endpoints to the backend

The backend is ONLY for:
- Knowledge base retrieval (POST /api/knowledge)
- Session logging (POST /api/sessions)
- Health check (GET /health)
